# Audit evidence (screenshots, scratch notes) — kept on disk for the
# operator to review, never committed (binary churn).
.audit/

# Claude Code + OpenAI Agents per-developer state. Skills live under
# `.claude/skills/` and `.agents/skills/` — both are intentionally
# kept OUT of git history because they evolve with each contributor's
# workflow and the OpenAI mirror has format-specific divergences
# (shorter description fields, separate openai.yaml manifests) that
# do not belong in shared repo history. New contributors bootstrap
# their own skill packs from a central registry, not from this repo.
.claude/skills/
.agents/skills/
.claude/worktrees/
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/launch.json
.claude/preview.json
